    <briefdescription>
<para>System that propagates high score snapshots to MaxScoreObserverComponents. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Each frame, queries all active entities with a MaxScoreObserverComponent and updates them with the current <ref refid="structhelios_1_1engine_1_1mechanics_1_1scoring_1_1MaxScorePoolSnapshot" kindref="compound">MaxScorePoolSnapshot</ref> from the <ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1mechanics_1_1scoring_1_1ScorePoolManager" kindref="compound">ScorePoolManager</ref>. The component&apos;s revision-based change detection ensures that downstream consumers (e.g. UI bindings) are only notified when the high score actually changes.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="see"><para><ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1mechanics_1_1scoring_1_1systems_1_1MaxScoreObserverClearSystem" kindref="compound">MaxScoreObserverClearSystem</ref> </para>
